Hi Mate,

It will be awesome if you could do something about our firefighters in NSW. They deserve our attention and our support. You've got more than 1million of subscribers... please!!!! It won't take you long to make a short video to support our heroes who fights 24h for our lives!!!! If you don't wanna reply here my Instagram is: mr_leaf_syd
I won't accept any add on my Insta as I'm not looking for that. I'm just a french frog who loves Australia and who wants help my new family.
Hope you'll answer me. And excuse me for my English guys.

snippet.textDisplay:
Our hopes for YBS in 2020: More informational videos like this one, maybe have Jarrad do a video once a month (if possible) to teach us about the different parts of the ecosystem that we may be overlooking when we go out to fish/explore that we could be accidentally harming so we know what mistakes to not make and what to do if we see a decline in our own local ecosystems so we can try to help restore it. Going to suggest maybe Q&A Videos once a month on a different topic, and with different members of the crew! We love Brodie but we also love Sam, Jacko, Jackie, Jarrad, etc! Much more Stryda dog, more overnight camping excursions with the old boy/others/solo, and MORE FIRE BABY!

I feel like you have one of the best platforms available to you these days, with the amount of subscribers, to make a really positive impact for the environment and reef systems not only surrounding Australia, but other parts of the world. Maybe 2020 can bring about the positive change for those precious ecosystems that we have fought long and hard to save/preserve. Thanks so much for entertaining all of us YBS Crew - from the bottom of our hearts we are ever so grateful for being including in your adventures and lifestyle!
